(211, 120, 164, 'Hi Nadine\nI''m wondering if you are still looking for a nanny??\nI would love the opportunity to speak with you to discuss your needs, and my experience working with children.\nPlease feel free to contact me directly on 0402010274\nRegards\nMeredith', 1),
