(113, 208, 216, 'Hi Shaylee,\n\nThank you for contacting me! I have found childcare for most days, though can I ask what area do you work in? Are one of you current nanny share client willing to continue sharing? If so what are  your hours and rates?\n\nThank you, Melissa'),
(114, 159, 216, 'Hi Shaylee,\n\nI didn''t realise my profile was still visible. We have found care. \n\nAll the best, \nLeanne'),
(115, 216, 208, 'Thanks for your reply Melissa, I live in the sutherland shire and travel to the city for work. Yes one of the families I work for on the thirsday/ friday live in daceyville and are looking for a share family :) $15 per hour per family.. I usually work 7:30-6:30 for one child and 8:30-4:30 for the other so hours are flexible :)'),
(116, 132, 216, 'Ha, no worries Shaylee!\nWe have found a lovely nanny for this year thank you.\nWe will need a new nanny come February, but I''m sure that will be too late!\nI''ll be in touch again later In the year anyway.\nThanks : ) Amber'),
(117, 216, 132, 'Thanks for your reply Amber, I am looking for a family next year! All my kids are going off to pre school :)'),
(118, 167, 216, 'Hi Shaylee, thanks very much for getting in touch! This sounds good and Id be interested in getting a few more details like where your other family lives/where you do the nanny share, and how old the child is. I currently have a nanny but we are still interested in seeing what share options are around, and my ideal days are Thurs Fri but I do have some flexibility. Thanks'),
(119, 167, 216, 'Hi shaylee, I just sent a message in rely but not sure if it has come through - let me know if not?'),
(120, 167, 216, 'Thanks for getting in touch! Sounds good. Where do you do the nanny share and how old is the other child? My ideal days are Thurs Fri, full days 8-6. And what''s your rate? We have a nanny but I''m still looking at share options closeby. Thanks again!'),
(121, 216, 167, 'Hi Angela, the little girl is 18 months and she lives in daceyville. The mum is very happy to have the care at her house and those hours work very well for us :) do you mind me asking where you live? And do you have any other questions for me?'),
(122, 109, 216, 'Hi Shaylee\n\nWe are still looking - we will need someone Wednesday''s and Thursday''s though - not sure if that suits your current arrangements?\n\nthanks\nNellie'),
(123, 217, 188, 'Hi Marissa, \nWe are looking to share a nanny for our 12 month old boy 2 days a week.  Would you be interested in sharing on a Monday and Wednesday? \nThanks\nSommer'),
(124, 216, 109, 'Thanks for your reply, I am available on Wednesdays and will have an opening on Thursdays for a nanny share arrangement if your interested? Starting in two weeks? May I ask what area you live in? Kind regards, shaylee'),
