(237, 'SineadG', 'Sinead', 'Goddard', 'sineadgoddard93@gmail.com', 'e0db638cc0c6700bddb491aca78f4613426084e0', 'e0db638cc0c6700bddb491aca78f4613426084e0', NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, '0000-00-00', '41A Old Berowra Road,Hornsby,NSW,2077', '8cfc4cd11d615275ae718071d6adeee6.JPG', '2077 Hornsby', 2, 'N/A', NULL, 0, '', 0, '', '4', '3-4-5-6-7', '2015-09-14', '1-2-3-4-5-6-7', 0, NULL, '30', '2', NULL, 0, NULL, '2', '1', NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, '5', '1', 'I know Auslan (Australian Sign Language)\n', 1, 'Hi Families :)\nMy name is Sinead and I have been working as a nanny for just over 5 years.\nIt believe it is important to work in partnership with the families and children I work with, to create a warm and nurturing environment that is enriched through play based learning and by recognising and promoting development according to each child''s individual needs.\nI believe that learning should take place naturally in an environment that offers a choice of activities created with the child''s needs, interests and abilities in mind. I believe that children learn about themselves and their world around them by being active participants in their play and learning, through touching, manipulating and experimenting with different materials and through their interactions with other children and adults. I also believe in the importance of focusing on the process of learning, rather than the end result.\n'),
